{"thig6.2:0.1":"Therigatha 6.2 ","thig6.2:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thig6.2:0.3":"Vasetthitherigatha ","thig6.2:1.1":"“Puttasokenaham atta, ","thig6.2:1.2":"khittacitta visannini; ","thig6.2:1.3":"Nagga pakinnakesi ca, ","thig6.2:1.4":"tena tena vicariham. ","thig6.2:2.1":"Vithi sankarakutesu, ","thig6.2:2.2":"susane rathiyasu ca; ","thig6.2:2.3":"Acarim tini vassani, ","thig6.2:2.4":"khuppipasasamappita. ","thig6.2:3.1":"Athaddasasim sugatam, ","thig6.2:3.2":"nagaram mithilam pati; ","thig6.2:3.3":"Adantanam dametaram, ","thig6.2:3.4":"sambuddhamakutobhayam. ","thig6.2:4.1":"Sacittam patiladdhana, ","thig6.2:4.2":"vanditvana upavisim; ","thig6.2:4.3":"So me dhammamadesesi, ","thig6.2:4.4":"anukampaya gotamo. ","thig6.2:5.1":"Tassa dhammam sunitvana, ","thig6.2:5.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","thig6.2:5.3":"Yunjanti satthuvacane, ","thig6.2:5.4":"sacchakasim padam sivam. ","thig6.2:6.1":"Sabbe soka samucchinna, ","thig6.2:6.2":"pahina etadantika; ","thig6.2:6.3":"Parinnata hi me vatthu, ","thig6.2:6.4":"yato sokana sambhavo”ti. ","thig6.2:7.1":"… Vasetthi theri …. "}